tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_error_correction_data ( 
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
    error_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, 
    error_occurrence_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, 
    correction_method VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
    correction_success BOOLEAN NOT NULL 
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_error_correction_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    error_type VARCHAR(50),
    correction_type VARCHAR(50),
    error_location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE correction_effectiveness (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    correction_id INT,
    effectiveness_score FLOAT,
    success_rate FLOAT,
    analysis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ErrorAnalysis (
  analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  event_id UUID,
  analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  error_cause TEXT,
  correction_effectiveness FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_error_correction_data (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_description TEXT,
    correction_method TEXT,
    error_date TIMESTAMP,
    correction_success BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE error_occurrence (
    occurrence_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_id INT,
    error_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    detector_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (error_id) REFERENCES quantum_error_correction_data (error_id)
);

CREATE TABLE correction_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_id INT,
    analysis_date TIMESTAMP,
    analysis_result TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (error_id) REFERENCES quantum_error_correction_data (error_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (error_id) REFERENCES quantum_error_correction_data (error_id)
);
